{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":574757,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"另外，dz打算最近不在树洞更新了。每日一曲在一堆只剩口号和meme的政治相关、只剩留号的性相关、无休止的争执和钓鱼里，在一堆hollow sound and fury里显得很尴尬，显得很不会读空气。不过我也是其中之一，没什么好说的。我一直在闭社和树洞同步更新，如果想追更的话欢迎移步闭社（）","timestamp":1605724421,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574759,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{"h":1500,"w":1500},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"图掉了吗","timestamp":1605724476,"type":"image","url":"ep/epowkohyqxwngifsr5ijnfgioly6htrx.jpeg"},{"cid":574764,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不过我演出前还是会来打下广告的×","timestamp":1605724585,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574766,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"希望dz早日回归qwq","timestamp":1605724643,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574787,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"每日一曲真的很好的呀，只是树洞太垃圾场了……哎（我也是垃圾一员）","timestamp":1605725239,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574791,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 你在闭社闲聊群","timestamp":1605725320,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574792,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"移步闭社？我很久没上树洞了，dz是公开过身份吗？","timestamp":1605725325,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574793,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 吗","timestamp":1605725331,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574799,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"啊，编号写成另一首间奏曲了。。应该是Op.117 No.2\n","timestamp":1605725558,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":574824,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: ？？","timestamp":1605726661,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":575064,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这两天刚听！","timestamp":1605748508,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":575070,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"啊哈哈我就说，我看dz的描述完全不像118 no2而更像117 no2来着","timestamp":1605748624,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":575111,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"对古典感点兴趣，想问下闭社是什么呢？","timestamp":1605749284,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":575126,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不过感觉更推荐卡钦的版本（\n","timestamp":1605749651,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":575460,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"毕设（x）闭社是啥哇","timestamp":1605755088,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":591997,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":119762,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"古尔德的版本也不错（","timestamp":1605911879,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":10,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":119762,"reply":16,"tag":null,"text":"#117420\n#每日一曲\n\n勃拉姆斯，间奏曲，Op.118 No.2\n之前听这首，虽然也听到了不安的隐流，但感觉总体还是平和的，仿佛带一层回忆往事的滤镜。可是今晚听时，猛然发现这里的情绪波动远比回忆强烈，更像是……\n怎么说呢，如果要配上画面的话，大概是，有条不紊地行动（工作/穿行）着的背景人群（这是第一主题下低声部流动的伴奏），其中有一个人，虽然表面努力维持和旁人一样行动，但却心事重重。主题里那么多的弱起音，每一次都简直就像是心里的疙瘩硌了一下、心结拧了一下。对了，这时应该是下着雨的，雨兼有秩序和不安的因素。每次织体切换成柱式和弦为主时，画面就变得凝滞起来，仿佛他终于停了下来开始出神，可能是心事压不住，也可能是什么外物吸引了他的注意。而每当流动的低声部再现，就是背景人群又出现在镜头中。\n不知道有没有描述清楚……总之就是一种看似平稳，实则局促之极、纠结之极的感受。今晚一点开这首，主题里那几个弱起音就瞬而把dz的心境带回到五年前的这时候，某个寡色的深秋下午，alas\n\nhttps://y.music.163.com/m/song/440310739","timestamp":1605724309,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782652,"url":"","vote":{}}}